high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the section of counter in between the oven and the fridge.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter in front of you.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left to face the counter.
Slice up the rightmost head of lettuce on the counter.
Put the butter knife on the front of the counter in front of you.
Pick up a piece of sliced lettuce off of the counter.
Turn left and walk over to the fridge.

Open the fridge and place the piece of sliced lettuce on the middle shelf, then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge and take the piece of lettuce back out, then close the fridge door.
Turn right and walk over to the small silver bin in the corner of the room.
Place the chilled piece of sliced lettuce in the back left corner of the silver bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled piece of sliced lettuce in a small bin.

high_descs: Turn around and look for the knife on the counter to your right.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Take a step to the right and find the lettuce next to the stove.
Cut the lettuce into several slices.
Place the knife in front of the fork.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn left and head towards the fridge on your right.
Open the fridge, place the lettuce inside for it to cool, and take it back out.
Turn right, head towards the wall, and then turn right towards the grey bin on the floor.
Place the lettuce in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool slice of lettuce in the grey bin.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fork and knife on your right.
Pick the knife up from the counter.
Look at the lettuce.
Cut the lettuce on the right side of the counter.
Put the knife down on the counter.
Pick up a piece of the lettuce you just cut.
Turn to your left and walk to the fridge.
Chill the lettuce in the refrigerator and then pick the lettuce back up.
Turn around and walk to the trash can in the opposite corner of where you are now.
Place the lettuce in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled piece of lettuce in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter between the fridge and stove.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Move over to the right to stand in front of the lettuce that is on the counter.
Use the knife to cut the lettuce into slices.
Put the butter knife down on the counter.
Pick up a slice of the lettuce.
Turn to the left and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the lettuce inside, close the fridge, open the fridge, remove the lettuce, close the fridge.
Turn to the right, go to the end of the room, take a right and go to the garbage can.
Put the lettuce in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of cold lettuce in a garbage can.

high_descs: Walk to the counter to the left of the stove and face it.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right, turn left to face the counter again.
Slice the right hand head of lettuce.
Put the knife on the counter.
Pick up one slice of the lettuce.
Turn left, walk to refrigerator, and face the refrigerator.
Put lettuce on the shelf in the refrigerator, close it, wait a bit, take the lettuce out of the refrigerator.
Turn right, walk to the wall, turn right, walk to the garbage can.
Throw lettuce in garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of lettuce in the garbage.
